      "title": "Sri Lanka stocks slip in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka shares fell within the first hour of trade on Thursday (30) after opening stronger, Colombo Stock Exchange data showed.",
        "The main All Share Price Index slipped 0.19 percent or 13.84 points to 7,352.08 at 1130 hours.",
        "The most liquid index was down 0.31 percent or 7.29 points to 2,342.99."
